Running pytests with 'hidden room' which contains all my tools like pytest,python,requests,playwright:
    poetry run pytest smoke_test.py -s
Run one specific test:
    poetry run pytest tests/database/test_user_persistance.py::test_update_table

Run Docker without logs
    docker-compose up -d

docker-compose down -v
    sposób na wyczyszczenie "starej pamięci" haseł w Postgresie.
